<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Excluir Usuário</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Excluir Usuário</h1>
        <p>Tem certeza que deseja excluir o usuário <strong><%= usuario.nome %></strong> (Email: <%= usuario.email %>)?</p>
        <form action="/usuarios/<%= usuario._id %>/remover" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger">Confirmar Exclusão</button>
            <a href="/usuarios/relatorio" class="btn btn-secondary ms-2">Cancelar</a>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
